ctx: Nemška ministrica: Visoki stroški ne bi smeli biti ovira za izločitev kitajske opreme iz omrežja G5
content:
SEveda ne, saj jih ne bo ona plačala ampak davkoplačevalci in
uporabniki storitev.
author: rx170

ctx: Nemška ministrica: Visoki stroški ne bi smeli biti ovira za izločitev kitajske opreme iz omrežja G5
content:
Kitajci bodo preživeli tudi brez nemških samoomejitev.

Primer kako so nadmudrili GPS:

Američani ugotavljajo, da Kitajci s svojim BeiDou sistemom
satelitske navigacije prehitevajo njihov GPS po ključnih
kriterijih, npr.:
- China’s BeiDou GNSS is newer, has more features, is more
accurate, and has more satellites in the skies of more nations than
the venerable U.S. GPS.
- The global reach of BeiDou ensures that China is no longer
dependent on another nation’s satnav. China’s economy — and those
of other nations relying on BeiDou — can continue to function even
if GPS is degraded or denied.
- The output of China’s commercial space and navigation services
industry has increased by tens of billions in the last
decade.
- BeiDou supports China’s Belt and Road and Digital Silk Road
initiatives to gain influence and leverage around the world.
- Itd.

Celotno poročilo je tukaj 
www.belfercenter.org...ou_V10.pdf
author: 0126Bacis
